  <title>Day 12：最差的一天 — 诸葛灯泡</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/style.css">
</head>
<body>

<nav class="nav">
  <a href="../index.html" class="nav-logo">
    <span class="bulb">💡</span>
    诸葛灯泡
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="../office.html">Office</a></li>
